{"tid":2223499,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"迪士尼大幅裁員","createTime":"2020-09-30T01:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T01:51:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98c9b5b779c890357d20e845a319a14cc45909f0","tid":2223499,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"迪士尼（Walt Disney，美：DIS）公布，將在美國境內的主題樂園裁員2.8萬人，因新冠肺炎疫情的影響，特別是加州的迪士尼樂園無法重開。迪士尼股價盤後跌1.4%，報123.65美元。<br />\n<br />\n被裁的員工屬於樂園、體驗及消費品部，迪士尼表示，被解雇的員工自4月以來一直放無薪假，其中約67%為兼職員工。迪士尼表示，將與工會就其成員的下一步行動展開討論。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼在佛羅里達州，巴黎，上海，日本及香港的主題公園已經有限度重新開放，不過加州的兩個主題樂園仍然關閉。迪士尼原本預計7月中重新開放樂園，惟加州政府不願解除限制，迪士尼於6月取消相關計劃。<br />\n<br />\n截至6月底止，迪士尼季度虧損47.2億美元，為近20年來首次錄得季度虧損，去年同期利潤為14.3億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2766288</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5b45f41e8818b047603693dce7bcf46ac431167a","tid":2223499,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"花木蘭呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a34c14407549cabc62f26ca286384ad1ce1f71","tid":2223499,"uid":14812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:18:48.000Z","msg":"出返兩套marvel賺返哂"},{"pid":"5efef4063d4989211cb8b918d8ecfa17784b30f3","tid":2223499,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30a34c14407549cabc62f26ca286384ad1ce1f71","tid":2223499,"uid":14812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:18:48.000Z","msg":"出返兩套marvel賺返哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"叫iron man死多兩次就得"},{"pid":"d8dd61913fb80a59705ec0a9e6f697f6fc6e95e5","tid":2223499,"uid":294632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"又可以溝貨DIS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f66bb77060d1abad3b125478e7a22191f45047","tid":2223499,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dis